&amp;modificationDate=1762593265985&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"255\" data-width=\"586\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"657260749\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"hippie_lighting_thumb.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"604667905\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" data-media-id=\"3623d112-e979-4e99-a975-6781f13617f2\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604667905/hippie_lighting_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762593265985&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604667905/hippie_lighting_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762593265985&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 1x\" /></span></a><p /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell aside\" data-type=\"aside\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h1 id=\"HippieTheForestDragon-Lighting\"><span data-colorid=\"dtpiu8yg6y\">Lighting</span></h1><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<hr /><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\" id=\"HippieTheForestDragon-AbouttheArtist\">About the Artist</h3><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.artstation.com/nidhivazzhala\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"nidhi-vazzhala-headshot.png\" width=\"198\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604667905/nidhi-vazzhala-headshot.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758110355812&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=198&amp;height=198\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/604667905/nidhi-vazzhala-headshot.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758110355812&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"512\" data-width=\"512\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"603914367\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"nidhi-vazzhala-headshot.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"604667905\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" data-media-id=\"9a3caca4-9a13-44f6-a97e-1b2cfbc3be72\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604667905/nidhi-vazzhala-headshot.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758110355812&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=396&amp;height=396 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604667905/nidhi-vazzhala-headshot.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758110355812&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=198&amp;height=198 1x\" /></span></a><p>I have always been an artistic person, so a profession related to art and creativity was my obvious career choice. I started my journey as a Graphic Designer, but there was something very fulfilling about creating 3d art that drew me closer to this industry and now I aspire to make a great career in 3d. I started working in this industry professionally as a Texturing and Lookdev artist at MPC Bangalore. Currently doing some freelance and working on upgrading my skills and portfolio. &nbsp;</p><p /><hr /><p>This project is available with an Attribution-NonCommercial 4.0 International License. This allows you to share and redistribute for non-commercial purposes, provided that you credit the original author.</p><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"35fd14dc-33bf-4f5e-a7b4-780e751ea2bb\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><h3 id=\"HippieTheForestDragon-Attribution-NonCommercial4.0International(CCBY-NC4.0)\">Attribution-NonCommercial 4.0 International (CC BY-NC 4.0)</h3></div></div><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"by-nc.png\" width=\"97\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604667905/by-nc.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758109607816&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=97&amp;height=33\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/604667905/by-nc.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758109607816&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"34\" data-width=\"97\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"604668047\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"by-nc.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"604667905\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" data-media-id=\"cf40859f-0255-43d3-bfee-8f358576f4ed\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604667905/by-nc.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758109607816&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=194&amp;height=66 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604667905/by-nc.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758109607816&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=97&amp;height=33 1x\" /></span><hr /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"co